                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def3-67a-18421128 t18421128-67a-punishment-62"></join>Con<lb></lb>fined Eighteen Months</rs>.</hi>—<hi rend="largeCaps">SMITH</hi>—
